'
' ============================================================================
' 毕业设计 · 单项功能 · 序号时序图（PlantUML）
' 规范：单色；矩形参与者；消息「序号. 中文说明」；实线→调用、虚线-->返回；
' diagrams.net ：调整图形 → 插入 → Advanced → PlantUML → 粘贴任一 @startuml…@enduml 整块
'
' 工程对齐：Secure Global Trade（Next.js Middleware + ApiHandler + CartProvider + Checkout）
' ============================================================================

@startuml seq_feature_search
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title 商品检索 · 序号时序（工程实现对齐）

participant "访客\n或买家" as User
participant "集合页视图\nTradeHome" as Page
participant "URL\nSearchParams" as Url
participant "目录快照\nlib/products" as Cat
participant "卡片\nnext/image" as Img

User -> Page: 1. 输入检索词「q」与/或类目「category」
activate Page

Page -> Url: 2. （设计中）防抖后同步 QueryString(q,category,page)

Url --> Page: 3. 回传分页与路由变化结果

Page -> Cat: 4. 子串近似匹配中英文案字段

Cat --> Page: 5. 返回筛选分页切片

Page -> Img: 6. 懒加载占位 + sizes 解码策略

Img --> Page: 7. 异步就绪（CDN 可协商 WebP/AVIF）

Page --> User: 8. 刷新网格与分页控件
deactivate Page

@enduml


@startuml seq_feature_cart
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title 购物车 · 序号时序（工程实现对齐）

participant "买家" as Buyer
participant "购物车上下文\nCartProvider" as Cart
participant "localStorage\nsgt-cart" as LS

Buyer -> Cart: 1. 加购 addToCart 或更改数量 remove/update
activate Cart

Cart -> LS: 2. 首次Hydration读取JSON（若损坏则忽略）

LS --> Cart: 3. 反序列化为 items 数组

Cart -> Cart: 4. 数量 clamp 为非负 · 数量为0则从数组剔除

Cart -> LS: 5. Hydrated 后写回整包 JSON（跨刷新一致）

Cart --> Buyer: 6. 回馈小计/件数，刷新抽屉视图
deactivate Cart

@enduml


@startuml seq_feature_checkout
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title 订单结算 · 序号时序（工程实现对齐）

participant "浏览器" as Br
participant "API门面\ncreateApiHandler" as Gate
participant "结账POST\napi/checkout" as Co
participant "会话服务\nSupabase Auth" as Auth
participant "订单表RLS\nPostgreSQL" as DB

Br -> Gate: 1. 提交购物车JSON序列化载荷
activate Gate

Gate -> Gate: 2. Zod safeParse · 字段白名单与数值界限

Gate -> Co: 3. 派发已解析 payloads
activate Co

note right of Gate
校验失败时在步骤2后直接返回：
HTTP 422 VALIDATION_FAILED
end note

Co -> Auth: 4. getUser()读取会话归属
activate Auth

Auth --> Co: 5. 返回 user.id · 或无会话401

deactivate Auth

Co -> Co: 6. 服务端重算 total_usd 防篡改小数

Co -> DB: 7. 参数化单行 INSERT （user_id取自会话）

DB --> Co: 8. 成功或无 RETURNING权限类错误码

Co --> Gate: 9. 附加 Set-Cookie 并返回结算JSON

deactivate Co

Gate --> Br: 10. HTTP 422/401/200/500 统一语义
deactivate Gate

@enduml


@startuml seq_feature_bruteforce
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title 暴力破解防御 · 令牌桶限速 · 序号时序（工程实现对齐）

participant "访客" as G
participant "Edge Middleware\n登录路径" as M
participant "速率桶 Map\nrouteTag:IP" as B
participant "登录路由\napi/auth/login" as L

G -> M: 1. POST 凭据到登录 API
activate M

M -> B: 2. consumeRateLimit:key 递减窗口额度

B --> M: 3. allowed / retryAfterSec / count

alt 窗口已满（拒绝）

M --> G: 4a. 429 + Retry-After + 可选写入 Brute-force 审计记录

else 窗口允许放行

M -> L: 4b. 透传原 POST 载荷

activate L

L --> G: 5. JSON 成败（口令校验）

deactivate L

end

deactivate M

@enduml


@startuml seq_feature_xss
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title URL-XSS Edge 封堵 · 序号时序（工程实现对齐）

participant "访客" as G
participant "Edge Middleware\ndecode+regex" as M
participant "403封堵页 HTML" as F

G -> M: 1. 携带可疑 QueryString / Path
activate M

M -> M: 2. 多重解码并匹配 XSS 关键字模式

alt 命中恶意片段
 M -> F: 3a. 组装品牌化 403 页面SEO no-index
 activate F

 F --> M: 附带 await·审计打点写 security_logs XSS

 deactivate F

 M --> G: 4a. Cache-Control:no-store HTTP403 HTML

else 未命中

 M --> G: 3b. 继续 Next / API 链路

end

deactivate M
@enduml


@startuml seq_feature_audit
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title SOC 共通订阅链路 · security_logs INSERT → Realtime · 对齐四模块落库后续

participant "四类安全派发点\n(edge/api)" as W
participant "security_logs\nPostgreSQL" as T
participant "Realtime\npublication" as R
participant "SOC仪表盘\nStatusDashboard" as D

W -> T: 1. INSERT结构化审计列（载荷截断/IP/严重程度…）
activate W
activate T

T --> W: 2. 确认插入或错误日志

deactivate T

T -> R: 3. replication 广播 INSERT 事件

R --> D: 4. client subscribe postgres_changes
activate R
activate D

D -> D: 5. 状态Hook刷新计数与最近 attack_type

deactivate D
deactivate R
deactivate W

note bottom of W
四模块任一成功 insert 皆可触发本条链路；Middleware 写入须 await 防 Edge 冻结丢审计。
end note

@enduml


@startuml seq_feature_auth_password
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title 安全模块 3 · 口令托管与认证失败审计 · 序号时序（对齐 login/route）

participant "浏览器" as B
participant "登录POST\n/api/auth/login" as L
participant "Zod闸门\n邮箱口令形" as Z
participant "Supabase Auth\nGoTrue会话" as A
participant "security_logs" as T

B -> L: 1. POST JSON(email,password)
activate L

L -> Z: 2. safeParse邮箱规范化与口令长度下限
activate Z
Z --> L: 3. issues则422且不触达口令比对
deactivate Z

L -> A: 4. signInWithPassword · 口令摘要比对（服务端托管 bcrypt 语义）
activate A
A --> L: 5. 返回会话user或INVALID错误对象
deactivate A

alt 口令错误或缺少user会话

 L -> T: 6a. insert Auth Failure·掩码邮箱·api防御层·denied
 activate T

 T --> L: ACK
 deactivate T

 L --> B: 7a. HTTP401 JSON INVALID_CREDENTIALS

else 认证成功

 L --> B: 6b. attachAuthCookies→200最小user投影

end

deactivate L

@enduml


@startuml seq_feature_schema_zod
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title 安全模块 4 · Zod契约拒绝链 · Schema Validation 审计（对齐 api-handler）

participant "浏览器" as B
participant "REST入口\ncreateApiHandler" as G
participant "Zod\nsafeParse投影" as Z
participant "recordSchema\nValidationAudit" as R
participant "PostgreSQL\nsecurity_logs" as T

B -> G: 1. POST JSON未知结构业务载荷
activate G

G -> Z: 2. Schema解析与精炼规则(safeText等)
activate Z

Z --> G: 3. success分支data或failure issues数组

alt 契约失败分支

 G -> R: 4a. await记录pathname+第一条issue概要
 activate R

 R -> T: INSERT event_type Schema Validation...
 activate T

 T --> R: ACK
 deactivate T

 R --> G
 deactivate R

 G --> B: 5a. 422 VALIDATION_FAILED + issues明文脱敏粒度受控

else 契约成功

 G --> B: (后续进入业务handler本图略)

end

deactivate Z
deactivate G

@enduml

